<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Notebook Entry</div>
<dl id="n06151c"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="n06" href="#n06151c">N06 (VI.B.11)</a>:  <a href="../../ff/fnbs/n06all.htm#n06151c"> 151(c)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> adopted child of God / put on <font face="wake">+</font></blockquote> <dd class="well"> <blockquote class="sources"><mark>&ldquo;THE CHILD OF GOD.&rdquo;&mdash;By adoption</mark>; taken out of the number of Adam&apos;s lost children, and taken into the number of God&apos;s children. This adoption is obtained by faith in Jesus Christ. For as many as have been baptized into Christ have <mark>put on Christ</mark>. <small> Anonymous, <a name="ATCC" href="../../ff/fdra/fdex.htm#ATCC"><cite title="source">Analysis of the Church Catechism</cite></a> (1879) 9</small></blockquote> </dd></dl>
